des: This station features the teaching and preaching of Dr. Larry Ollison, pastor of the Walk on the Water Faith Church in Osage Beach, Missouri. Larry has ministered the Word of Faith for over 60 years. He is in great demand as a conference speaker and is the author of ten books including his latest release, \"Hidden Mysteries and the Bible.\"
